 151:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.c **** /**
 152:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.c ****   * @brief  Reset the RCC clock configuration to the default reset state.
 153:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.c ****   * @note   The default reset state of the clock configuration is given below:
 154:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.c ****   *         - HSI ON and used as system clock source
 155:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.c ****   *         - HSE and PLL OFF
 156:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.c ****   *         - AHB and APB1 prescaler set to 1.
 157:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.c ****   *         - CSS, MCO OFF
 158:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.c ****   *         - All interrupts disabled
 159:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.c ****   * @note   This function does not modify the configuration of the
 160:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.c ****   *         - Peripheral clocks
 161:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.c ****   *         - LSI, LSE and RTC clocks
 162:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.c ****   * @retval An ErrorStatus enumeration value:
