3122:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.h **** /**
3123:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.h ****   * @brief  Enable PLL output mapped on ADC domain clock
3124:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.h ****   * @rmtoll PLLCFGR      PLLPEN        LL_RCC_PLL_EnableDomain_ADC
3125:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.h ****   * @note   User shall check that PLL enable is not done through
