3134:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.h **** /**
3135:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.h ****   * @brief  Disable PLL output mapped on ADC domain clock
3136:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_rcc.h ****   * @note Cannot be disabled if the PLL clock is used as the system clock
